Excellent ‚Äî here‚Äôs a **fully fleshed-out, executive-ready 10-minute presentation on Agentic AI** with **detailed narrative for each slide**.
This script is designed so you can **read or paraphrase directly** during the presentation.
It connects the historical evolution of AI, the mechanics of agentic systems, and **concrete financial use cases**, with every point backed by reputable sources.

